  * Added symbols.c:disable_all_breakpoints
  * Added ``process.[ch]'': init_sighandler, pid2proc
  * Removed ``trace.c''
  * Added rudimentary support for multiple processes
  * Now tracing syscalls (fork() needs a special treatment (TODO))
